{"source": "https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/pinglun/tengbiao/tb2-05302023133004.html", "type": "NewsArticle", "published time": "2023-05-30T13:52:00-04:00", "modified time": "2023-05-30T18:14:46-04:00", "author": null, "publisher": {"type": "Organization", "name": "Radio Free Asia"}, "title": "\u8bc4\u8bba | \u6ed5\u5f6a\uff1a\u6781\u6743\u4e0e\u7b11\u8bdd\uff08\u4e0b\uff09", "description": "\u6781\u6743\u8bed\u8a00\u7684\u7d22\u7136\u65e0\u5473\uff0c\u6781\u6743\u601d\u60f3\u7684\u9ed1\u767d\u98a0\u5012\uff0c\u6781\u6743\u827a\u672f\u7684\u77eb\u63c9\u9020\u4f5c\uff0c\u6781\u6743\u6587\u5316\u7684\u8c04\u5a9a\u7c97\u66b4\u3001\u5047\u5927\u7a7a\uff0c\u4f7f\u5f97\u4efb\u4f55\u6709\u72ec\u7acb\u601d\u8003\u548c\u5ba1\u7f8e\u80fd\u529b\u7684\u4eba\u90fd\u96be\u4ee5\u5fcd\u53d7\u3002", "videos": [], "audios": ["https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/pinglun/tengbiao/tb2-05302023133004.html/@@stream"], "text": "<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/pinglun/tengbiao/tb2-05302023133004.html/@@images/c1ff968e-3e41-41b7-9b54-f7f6e4d07a01.jpeg\"/>\n2023\u5e745\u670817\u65e5\uff0c\u4e0a\u6d77\u4e00\u5bb6\u5267\u9662\u5916\u7b11\u679c\u8131\u53e3\u79c0\u7684\u6807\u5fd7\u3002\n\u6cd5\u65b0\u793e\u56fe\u7247\n<!-- zoomattribute -->\n<script language=\"javascript\" type=\"text/javascript\">\n var audio_title = {\"audio_name\": \"\\u8bc4\\u8bba | \\u6ed5\\u5f6a\\uff1a\\u6781\\u6743\\u4e0e\\u7b11\\u8bdd\\uff08\\u4e0b\\uff09\"};\n</script>\n<script>\n eventer = function(id){\n            var data = {\n                    \"tealium_event\" : \"audio_play\",\n                    \"on_page_event\" : \"audio_play\",\n                    \"audio_name\": audio_title['audio_name'],\n                    \"article_uid\": utag_data[\"article_uid\"],\n                    \"media_type\": \"onDemand audio\",\n                    \"media_name\": \"audio\",\n                    \"me_content_type\": utag_data[\"content_type\"],\n                    \"section\": utag_data[\"section\"],\n                    \"